1316
01:42:00.300 --> 01:42:03.800 line:82%
He has come and he has
come with a sword.

1317
01:42:03.890 --> 01:42:04.970 line:82%
Pooja.

1318
01:42:10.850 --> 01:42:12.640 line:82%
Thanks. See you tomorrow.

1319
01:42:12.720 --> 01:42:14.470 line:82%
-Pooja.
-What?

1320
01:42:16.350 --> 01:42:19.220 line:82%
It's that story you
told me at Soni's.

1321
01:42:19.850 --> 01:42:22.930 line:82%
That some special girl
is made for me etc, etc

1322
01:42:23.430 --> 01:42:24.850 line:82%
I've been thinking about that.

1323
01:42:26.300 --> 01:42:29.100 line:82%
-I don't get something.
-What?

1324
01:42:30.720 --> 01:42:34.640 line:82%
How would I know
who's made for me?

1325
01:42:34.930 --> 01:42:37.010 line:82%
You have so much faith
in this theory.

1326
01:42:37.100 --> 01:42:39.850 line:82%
I'm sure that you know about
how I'm going to meet this girl.

1327
01:42:40.100 --> 01:42:44.800 line:82%
I mean, will she be holding
a placard with my name on it?

1328
01:42:45.100 --> 01:42:47.180 line:82%
Or, when I see her would
there be a clap of thunder

1329
01:42:47.260 --> 01:42:48.800 line:82%
and a bolt of lightning?

1330
01:42:48.890 --> 01:42:50.640 line:82%
Would music play?
What?

1331
01:42:51.970 --> 01:42:53.430 line:82%
He will tell you.

1332
01:42:53.970 --> 01:42:55.800 line:82%
He will give just one sign

1333
01:42:55.890 --> 01:42:58.640 line:82%
and your heart
would recognise the girl.

1334
01:47:17.460 --> 01:47:20.210 line:82%
I've tried reasoning with her
but she just wouldn't listen.

1335
01:47:20.630 --> 01:47:22.420 line:82%
-She does what she wants.
-Hi, Doctor.

1336
01:47:22.500 --> 01:47:25.250 line:82%
-Doctor.
-Rahul, it is good that you came.

1337
01:47:25.300 --> 01:47:28.000 line:82%
-I'm fed up with this girl.
-Why? What happened?

1338
01:47:28.090 --> 01:47:32.420 line:82%
I told her clearly that she needs
to stay at home to rest.

1339
01:47:32.500 --> 01:47:36.000 line:82%
But look at her, she's packing
her bags to go somewhere.

1340
01:47:36.090 --> 01:47:38.670 line:82%
-Where to?
-How would I know?

1341
01:47:38.750 --> 01:47:41.420 line:82%
I've tried my best to explain.
She doesn't listen to me.

1342
01:47:41.500 --> 01:47:43.750 line:82%
You're the only one
who could convince her.

1343
01:47:43.840 --> 01:47:46.130 line:82%
Don't worry as she won't
go anywhere.

1344
01:47:46.210 --> 01:47:47.550 line:82%
I'll go in, take her
to task now.

1345
01:47:47.630 --> 01:47:50.090 line:82%
-Okay? -Best of luck.
-Okay, see you. -Bye.

1346
01:47:51.960 --> 01:47:53.000 line:82%
Nisha.

1347
01:47:55.880 --> 01:47:58.670 line:82%
