Are you nuts?

1348
01:47:58.750 --> 01:48:00.420 line:82%
The doctor told you to rest, right?

1349
01:48:00.500 --> 01:48:02.380 line:82%
By the way,
where are you off to?

1350
01:48:02.460 --> 01:48:04.750 line:82%
-I'm going to London.
-London?

1351
01:48:04.920 --> 01:48:07.750 line:82%
Well, Mom and Dad keep calling me

1352
01:48:07.840 --> 01:48:09.920 line:82%
