since I met them.

1353
01:48:10.710 --> 01:48:12.130 line:82%
I thought I'd visit them.

1354
01:48:12.210 --> 01:48:15.130 line:82%
Besides, I want to
run away from here.

1355
01:48:15.460 --> 01:48:17.340 line:82%
