was saying.

1372
01:49:19.250 --> 01:49:24.340 line:82%
Actually, Rahul, we've
become such good friends

1373
01:49:25.550 --> 01:49:27.960 line:82%
that we take each other
for granted.

1374
01:49:29.170 --> 01:49:34.880 line:82%
So I think that a bit of space
will give us time to think.

1375
01:49:36.960 --> 01:49:38.840 line:82%
But I'm sure

1376
01:49:39.340 --> 01:49:44.210 line:82%
that when I'm not here,
you'll miss me a lot.

1377
01:49:44.880 --> 01:49:47.550 line:82%
Then maybe then
you'd realise my worth.

1378
01:49:47.880 --> 01:49:52.000 line:82%
One thing is certain
that an idiot like you

1379
01:49:52.090 --> 01:49:54.500 line:82%
doesn't deserve a girl like me.

1380
01:49:55.630 --> 01:49:59.340 line:82%
And I don't know why,
but I feel that

1381
