I may not be in the mood for it.

1384
01:50:12.170 --> 01:50:13.550 line:82%
Get lost.

1385
01:50:13.630 --> 01:50:15.210 line:82%
Well, maybe you
haven't seen your face

1386
01:50:15.300 --> 01:50:16.500 line:82%
It's better than yours.

1387
01:50:17.670 --> 01:50:22.460 line:82%
-Hey, Nisha
-Rahul.

1388
01:50:30.050 --> 01:50:33.880 line:82%
Nisha, you're really nice.

1389
01:50:35.130 --> 01:50:36.750 line:82%
I know. Come now.

1390
01:50:36.840 --> 01:50:39.090 line:82%
I must meet everyone on
my way to the airport.

1391
01:50:39.300 --> 01:50:40.800 line:82%
Come on, Rahul. Hurry up.

1392
01:50:47.960 --> 01:50:49.710 line:82%
-We'll see you.
-Bye, see you guys.

1393
01:50:49.800 --> 01:50:51.960 line:82%
-Take care.
-I'll really miss you. -Thanks.

1394
01:50:52.050 --> 01:50:54.460 line:82%
-Bye.
-Enjoy yourself.

1395
01:50:54.550 --> 01:50:57.250 line:82%
-Take care.
-Bye Nisha. -Bye buddy.

1396
01:50:57.300 --> 01:50:58.960 line:82%
Rahul, has our stuff arrived?

1397
01:50:59.050 --> 01:51:01.550 line:82%
Ballu is mad.

1398
