Let's start from the beginning.

1400
01:51:10.170 --> 01:51:12.420 line:82%
-Hi! I'm Nisha.
-I'm Pooja.

1401
01:51:13.300 --> 01:51:15.340 line:82%
Now that we are friends

1402
01:51:15.710 --> 01:51:20.210 line:82%
will you forgive me
for what I did yesterday?

1403
01:51:20.300 --> 01:51:22.670 line:82%
Forgive you? For what?

1404
01:51:22.920 --> 01:51:27.460 line:82%
Pooja, what I did with you
yesterday wasn't right.

1405
01:51:28.340 --> 01:51:31.500 line:82%
Actually, ever since
this place was built

1406
01:51:32.340 --> 01:51:34.550 line:82%
I've been the only one
who's danced on this floor.

1407
01:51:35.300 --> 01:51:37.550 line:82%
This floor has become my identity.

1408
01:51:38.050 --> 01:51:44.550 line:82%
So when I heard that someone else
had taken my place I felt bad.

1409
01:51:45.300 --> 01:51:48.710 line:82%
Without seeing you or
knowing you, I was jealous.

1410
01:51:49.710 --> 01:51:51.800 line:82%
I shouldn't have felt that way.

1411
01:51:52.250 --> 01:51:55.170 line:82%
Had I been in your place,
I'd have done the same.

1412
01:51:55.710 --> 01:51:59.000 line:82%
Moreover, I really enjoyed
dancing with you.

1413
01:51:59.670 --> 01:52:01.550 line:82%
You were the one dancing.

1414
01:52:02.460 --> 01:52:03.960 line:82%
I was doing something else.

1415
01:52:05.630 --> 01:52:07.750 line:82%
-I'm really sorry, Pooja.
-It's okay

1416
01:52:07.840 --> 01:52:10.250 line:82%
Come on. The pilot
just called for you.

1417
01:52:10.380 --> 01:52:15.050 line:82%
I always told Rahul that there could
never be another dancer like me.

1418
01:52:15.420 --> 01:52:16.670 line:82%
But I can't say that any more.

1419
01:52:17.750 --> 01:52:19.420 line:82%
And I'm sure that

1420
01:52:19.500 --> 01:52:22.460 line:82%
no one can play the role
of Maya better than you.

1421
01:52:22.630 --> 01:52:24.840 line:82%
Not even me. All the best.

1422
01:52:24.920 --> 01:52:26.300 line:82%
-Bye. See you.
-Thank you! Bye.

1423
01:52:26.340 --> 01:52:27.420 line:82%
Come.

