felt you would be ideal for this.

1429
01:53:37.590 --> 01:53:39.500 line:82%
Check, check 69

1430
01:53:39.590 --> 01:53:42.380 line:82%
Ballu, what are you doing?
Throw the spotlight properly.

1431
01:53:43.300 --> 01:53:47.090 line:82%
Pooja, good, good. But

1432
01:53:48.380 --> 01:53:51.750 line:82%
I think that you are not
opening up.

1433
01:53:52.170 --> 01:53:55.500 line:82%
I want to see how Maya
looks when she's happy.

1434
01:53:55.670 --> 01:53:59.920 line:82%
I want to see the zenith of
Maya's passion and love. Okay?

1435
01:54:01.000 --> 01:54:03.170 line:82%
Do it again. Okay.

1436
01:54:04.000 --> 01:54:06.750 line:82%
Quiet everybody.
Take it from the top.

1437
01:54:07.630 --> 01:54:08.750 line:82%
Music!

1438
01:54:09.670 --> 01:54:11.000 line:82%
Cut it! Cut it!

1439
01:54:11.210 --> 01:54:12.630 line:82%
I told you to forget
your identity

1440
01:54:12.750 --> 01:54:14.710 line:82%
and forget that there
are people sitting here.

1441
01:54:14.800 --> 01:54:15.960 line:82%
Forget about the rehearsal.

1442
01:54:16.050 --> 01:54:17.340 line:82%
But you refuse to understand.

1443
01:54:17.420 --> 01:54:18.500 line:82%
Pack up.

1444
01:54:21.420 --> 01:54:23.340 line:82%
I don't get one thing, Pooja.

1445
01:54:24.420 --> 01:54:27.380 line:82%
How would I know which
girl was made for me?

1446
01:54:27.800 --> 01:54:30.340 line:82%
Will she be holding a placard
with my name on it?

1447
01:54:30.420 --> 01:54:32.630 line:82%
When I see her, would
there be a clap of thunder

1448
01:54:32.710 --> 01:54:34.250 line:82%
and a flash of lightning?

1449
01:56:21.000 --> 01:56:26.960 line:82%
Oh dear, what's happening?
I really don't know.

1450
01:56:27.500 --> 01:56:33.710 line:82%
I only hope this does not
turn into a tale of love.

1451
01:56:33.920 --> 01:56:39.800 line:82%
Oh dear, what's going on?
Nobody really knows.

1452
01:56:40.420 --> 01:56:46.420 line:82%
But if this is a tale
of love, then so be it.

1453
