Even the dewdrops seem to burn,
with the fever of my heart.

1460
01:58:20.250 --> 01:58:26.550 line:82%
Why do I feel as if
someone has caressed me

1461
01:58:26.630 --> 01:58:29.710 line:82%
Oh dear, what's going on?

1462
