Oh dear, what's going on?

1465
01:58:42.800 --> 01:58:45.840 line:82%
Nobody really knows.

1466
01:58:46.050 --> 01:58:48.840 line:82%
But if this is a tale of love

1467
01:58:48.920 --> 01:58:51.840 line:82%
then so be it.

1468
01:59:21.590 --> 01:59:26.750 line:82%
Please move away for a while,
so I can collect my feelings

1469
01:59:27.800 --> 01:59:33.090 line:82%
and calm the violent
beating of my heart.

1470
01:59:34.340 --> 01:59:40.630 line:82%
Let's slow down so that we
don't move ahead of time.

1471
01:59:40.750 --> 01:59:46.960 line:82%
Oh dear, what's happening?
Nobody really knows.

1472
01:59:53.670 --> 01:59:58.840 line:82%
There is something between us.
So don't deny it.

1473
02:00:00.130 --> 02:00:05.460 line:82%
And no one knows
how far it would go.

1474
02:00:06.590 --> 02:00:12.750 line:82%
For you should know that your
heart is not what it was.

1475
