I only hope this does not

1482
02:00:35.380 --> 02:00:38.000 line:82%
turn into a tale of love.

1483
02:01:08.000 --> 02:01:11.000 line:82%
I hope your uncle would be asleep
and I won't have to hear him sing.

1484
02:01:14.130 --> 02:01:15.250 line:82%
-Bye.
-Bye

1485
02:01:17.920 --> 02:01:20.500 line:82%
-Rahul, I forgot to tell you.
-What?

1486
02:01:20.590 --> 02:01:23.300 line:82%
-I can't attend rehearsal tomorrow.
-Why?

1487
02:01:23.460 --> 02:01:26.130 line:82%
-Tomorrow I'm going to Khandala.
-Khandala? Why?

1488
02:01:26.340 --> 02:01:29.050 line:82%
-My sister lives there.
-Which sister?

1489
02:01:29.500 --> 02:01:31.090 line:82%
She's my dance teacher.

1490
02:01:31.340 --> 02:01:34.460 line:82%
She taught me everything I know.

1491
02:01:34.550 --> 02:01:36.170 line:82%
It's her birthday tomorrow.

1492
02:01:37.000 --> 02:01:39.710 line:82%
If I say no, will you not go?

1493
02:01:41.380 --> 02:01:46.210 line:82%
I'd go anyway, but if you
said yes, I'd go happily.

1494
02:01:48.170 --> 02:01:51.130 line:82%
I'm joking. Go on. I'll look
into the other jobs tomorrow.

1495
02:01:51.210 --> 02:01:53.630 line:82%
-Thanks. Bye.
-Bye.

1496
02:01:59.130 --> 02:02:00.550 line:82%
Rahul is finished.

1497
02:02:15.710 --> 02:02:17.840 line:82%
-Rahul? What are you doing here?
-Hi.

1498
02:02:18.420 --> 02:02:21.170 line:82%
I have a friend in Khandala.
He's been calling me for ages

1499
02:02:21.250 --> 02:02:22.630 line:82%
but I've never had
a chance to go.

1500
02:02:22.710 --> 02:02:25.170 line:82%
And since we can't work
without you

1501
02:02:25.250 --> 02:02:27.250 line:82%
I thought I'd meet him,
and give you a ride too.

1502
02:02:27.340 --> 02:02:30.550 line:82%
As it is you're going alone,
so I thought you'd have company.

1503
02:02:30.630 --> 02:02:31.920 line:82%
Don't stare. Hurry up.

1504
02:02:32.000 --> 02:02:34.130 line:82%
If we go early we'll beat
the traffic. Come on.

1505
02:02:35.170 --> 02:02:38.210 line:82%
Well, why are you smiling?

1506
02:02:38.300 --> 02:02:40.130 line:82%
Nothing. Let's go.

1507
02:02:40.210 --> 02:02:42.710 line:82%
Today I'm really missing
my friend. Really!

1508
02:03:00.960 --> 02:03:04.090 line:82%
-Tommy, Ceasar, quiet! Quiet!
-Pooja, I'm scared of dogs.

1509
02:03:04.170 --> 02:03:06.840 line:82%
-Pooja, Get them off me.
-They won't do anything.

1510
02:03:07.130 --> 02:03:10.460 line:82%
Sister's taking a dance class there.
I'll just go and surprise her.

1511
02:03:10.550 --> 02:03:12.630 line:82%
Stay here. Don't worry,
they won't bite you.

1512
02:03:12.740 --> 02:03:14.250 line:82%
-I'll be back.
-Tommy, please.

1513
02:03:14.340 --> 02:03:17.460 line:82%
Want some soft drink?
You can have these flowers too.

1514
02:03:29.750 --> 02:03:32.800 line:82%
Sandhya, what are you doing?
I'll give you one now.

1515
02:03:32.880 --> 02:03:35.800 line:82%
You've put on so much weight,
and you can hardly move.

1516
02:03:35.840 --> 02:03:40.130 line:82%
No more chocolates and ice creams
for you. Get it right this time.

1517
02:03:42.840 --> 02:03:45.590 line:82%
Move the neck. Arms straight.

1518
02:03:45.670 --> 02:03:49.590 line:82%
You Why are you laughing?
Shut your mouth.

1519
02:03:50.000 --> 02:03:53.420 line:82%
If anyone gets it wrong then
no one will watch TV tonight.

1520
02:03:53.500 --> 02:03:55.880 line:82%
Don't come begging to me again
saying, please sister.

1521
02:03:55.960 --> 02:03:58.210 line:82%
Please Sister, let me watch TV.

1522
02:03:58.670 --> 02:04:01.130 line:82%
Look. There comes your dear Pooja.

1523
02:04:01.750 --> 02:04:03.670 line:82%
Sister, how did you recognize me?

1524
02:04:03.800 --> 02:04:05.800 line:82%
There's no need to act smart.

1525
02:04:05.880 --> 02:04:08.550 line:82%
I know all my girls from
the sound of their footsteps.

1526
02:04:08.630 --> 02:04:10.960 line:82%
Happy Birthday to you!

1527
02:04:11.050 --> 02:04:13.960 line:82%
What's this? You've brought me
